include LICENSE
include README.md
include README.zh-CN.md
include CHANGELOG.md
include CONTRIBUTING.md
include CONTRIBUTING.zh-CN.md

recursive-include docs *.md *.svg
recursive-include docs/evidence *.json *.jsonl
